Tidak akan.

745
01:22:52,801 --> 01:22:53,844
Kumohon jangan.

746
01:23:25,751 --> 01:23:27,419
Nenek.

747
01:23:34,259 --> 01:23:36,011
Nenek baik-baik saja?

748
01:23:36,428 --> 01:23:38,013
Aku bermimpi buruk.

