01:28:30,388 --> 01:28:31,890
Ada sesuatu untukmu.

818
01:29:17,978 --> 01:29:19,563
Peter.

819
01:29:20,939 --> 01:29:22,607
Bawa aku pergi dari sini.

820
01:29:32,200 --> 01:29:33,285
Dia menggigitku.

821
01:29:40,959 --> 01:29:42,294
Saat bulan bersinar...

822
01:29:45,171 --> 01:29:46,965
...aku akan jadi seperti dia.

823
01:29:50,135 --> 01:29:51,720
