01:33:26,399 --> 01:33:27,900
Peter.

837
01:33:31,112 --> 01:33:32,447
Aku harus pergi.

838
01:33:33,364 --> 01:33:35,032
Kau takkan aman bersamaku...

839
01:33:35,158 --> 01:33:37,952
...sampai aku belajar
cara melindungimu dari....

